"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/04\/big-belly-punishment-not-blessing\/","url_meta":{"origin":24220,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Gluttony: A large belly is a punishment, not a blessing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 4, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hasan reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, saw a man with a large belly and he said, \u201cWhat is this?\u201d The man said, \u201cIt is a blessing from Allah.\u201d Umar said, \u201cNo, rather it is a punishment.\u201d Source: H\u0323adi\u0304th Muh\u0323ammad ibn \u2018Abd Alla\u0304h al-Ans\u0323a\u0304ri\u0304 42 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20817,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/11\/umar-khalifah-favors-jew\/","url_meta":{"origin":24220,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Judgment: The Caliph judges in favor of the Jew","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn al-Musayyib reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, was presented with a dispute between a Muslim and a Jew. Umar believed that the truth was on the side of the Jew, so he passed judgment in his favor. The Jew said to him, \u201cBy Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hik